data.description: Enjoy your privacy in this stunning residence on a corner lot at the end of a quiet street in the Pheasant Run Subdivision. This home boasts four bedrooms and two full baths, AND a separate office featuring charming barn doors. The master bedroom is spacious and luxurious, featuring an en-suite bath with an elegant tile shower and glass door, double sinks, a relaxing jetted tub, and an expansive wrap-around walk-in closet. Each of the additional bedrooms also offers ample space with generously sized walk-in closets.  The kitchen is beautiful with its two-toned design, providing plenty of cabinet space with soft-closing doors, a generously sized pantry, stainless steel appliances, and elegant granite countertops.  This home truly stands out with the large 3 car garage space, with room in attic as well. French doors lead to enclosed back patio and fire pit area in the very spacious backyard. New Roof 2023! Don't miss this one!
